data.description: *NEW PRICE* *SUBFLOOR FIXED* *NEW CARPET UPSTAIRS* This stunning 4 bed/3 bath home is located in the highly sought after Talavera community! This custom one owner home offers an open floorplan to accommodate large gatherings which features a large living/dining room, high ceilings, beautiful archways, custom cabinetry, stained wood trim, and custom paint throughout. There are three spacious bedrooms and an office downstairs with the fourth bedroom/bonus room upstairs. The beautiful open kitchen offers a center island, stainless steel appliances, hammered copper farmhouse and prep sinks, and granite countertops ready for the chef in your family. The master ensuite offers a relaxing oasis that includes a jetted tub, walk-in shower, and large closet. The 3-car tandem garage offers ample space for all your toys or weekend warrior projects. Just minutes away from I-35, downtown, and Tinker AFB. Call today to schedule your private showing!
